{"prompt": "Develop a robust online platform for a construction management firm. The primary color should be a grounded earthy brown.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Construction Management</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #5a3e36; /* Earthy Brown */\n            --secondary-color: #d4c9c3; /* Lighter earthy tone */\n            --accent-color: #a3918a; /* A slightly darker variation */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --dark-text-color: #333333;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2, h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(90, 62, 54, 0.7), rgba(90, 62, 54, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/5a3e36/ffffff?text=Construction+Excellence') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            height: 50vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 1rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .card-container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 280px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .card p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 1rem);\n            padding: 0.7rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Apex Construction Management</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#projects\">Projects</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Building Your Vision, With Precision and Care</h2>\n        <p>Your trusted partner for seamless construction management, from concept to completion.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"card-container\">\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Project Planning & Design</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive planning, budgeting, and design coordination to lay a solid foundation for success.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Construction Execution</h3>\n                    <p>Efficient on-site management, quality control, and adherence to timelines and safety standards.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Procurement & Logistics</h3>\n                    <p>Streamlined sourcing of materials and management of supply chains for timely delivery.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Risk Management</h3>\n                    <p>Proactive identification and mitigation of potential risks to ensure project stability.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"projects\">\n            <h2>Featured Projects</h2>\n            <div class=\"card-container\">\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Modern Residential Complex</h3>\n                    <p>Delivered on time and within budget, a testament to meticulous planning and execution.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Commercial Office Space</h3>\n                    <p>Transforming raw spaces into functional and inspiring work environments.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Infrastructure Development</h3>\n                    <p>Contributing to community growth through robust and sustainable infrastructure projects.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Apex Construction Management</h2>\n            <p>At Apex Construction Management, we pride ourselves on a foundation of integrity, expertise, and a relentless commitment to client satisfaction. Our team of seasoned professionals brings years of experience across a diverse range of construction projects, ensuring that every undertaking is managed with the utmost precision and efficiency. We believe in building more than just structures; we build lasting relationships based on trust and delivering exceptional results.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-form\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have a project in mind or need expert advice? Contact us today.</p>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Construction Management. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}